pg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184404306/image_184404306.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">samvaltenbergs</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Silver has been a precious metal used by humanity for many centuries. Once used a currency and still sought after as a prized touch on jewelry products, it does have many other lesser-known key uses. Silver is highly conductive, playing a vital</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184404306/image_184404306.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745499-slvp-silver-production-is-not-growing", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:36:28", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745506", "title": "How Would A Government Shutdown Affect Market Volatility?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electronic highway billboard with government shutdown ahead warning\" data-id=\"1669041839\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Stephen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Brian Levitt, Global Market Strategist</em></p> <p>With much of the country looking ahead to the holidays, the US government could be on the verge of a shutdown. Congress, urged by incoming president Donald Trump, opposed a three-month extension to the current budget. Without</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1669041839/image_1669041839.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745506-how-government-shutdown-affect-market-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745496", "title": "Western Union: Deep Value And Dividend Income", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Western Union Office in Prague.\" data-id=\"1943169915\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">VIDOK</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The Western Union Company provides money movement and payment services worldwide, focused mostly on consumer cross border money transfers and consumer financial services including bill payment, money orders, and digital wallets. The company started out in communication services but has transformed over</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1943169915/image_1943169915.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745496-western-union-deep-value-and-dividend-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:15:15", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745502", "title": "Could A New Misery Index Help Explain The Election Outcome?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oversized vote and ballot box surrounded by people\" data-id=\"2158306529\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In 1970, everyone was feeling bad about the economy. How bad? To put a number to the pervasively negative vibe, Arthur Okun created the \"misery index:\" the sum of inflation and unemployment rates.</p> <p>But now everyone is puzzled. Why</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158306529/image_2158306529.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745502-new-misery-index-help-explain-election-outcome", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 10:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745493", "title": "Micron Q1 Review: Strong AI Demand Means I'm Still Bullish (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Taiwan Micron Technology Company plant.\" data-id=\"1660789089\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1660789089/image_1660789089.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BING-JHEN HONG/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Micron Technology (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) fell 16% following earnings, with their Q2 2025 revenue guidance of $7.7 billion to $8.1 billion missing estimates and driving the selloff. This was well <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387691-micron-tumbles-weak-q2-forecast-fails-to-overcome-q1-results\">below</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/