Thesis</h2> <p><strong>Quipt Home Medical (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QIPT\" title=\"Quipt Home Medical Corp.\">QIPT</a></span>)</strong> is one of those under-the-radar companies that answers a need in people\u2019s daily life by delivering in-home respiratory care and durable medical equipment to 135 centers in 26 states. They\u2019re all about respirators, and with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1291085789/image_1291085789.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745492-struggling-for-air-quipt-home-medical-stock-growth-hurdles-recovery-potential-hold-for-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 09:47:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745498", "title": "CB Leading Economic Index: Small Rise In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man in a business meeting using an interactive screen while giving a presentation\" data-id=\"1468025006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1468025006/image_1468025006.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1